# Optional: a free Cesium ion token unlocks the higher-quality "ion-world"
# terrain and Cesium OSM Buildings paths. The app works fully WITHOUT this —
# the default config uses only keyless free data. Get a free token at
# https://cesium.com/ion/  then copy this file to `.env`.
VITE_CESIUM_ION_TOKEN=

# Optional: override the GitHub Pages base path if you fork to a different
# repo name. Defaults to /world/.
# VITE_BASE=/your-repo/
